| 4 | No global error handler | Added 4-argument error middleware |
| 5 | No 404 handler | Added catch-all 404 route |
| 6 | Hardcoded port | Read from `process.env.PORT` |
| 7 | Timestamp in `/health` | Removed to reduce information leakage |
| 8 | Error details in prod | Conditionally hide stack traces based on `NODE_ENV` |

